Author: filsid
Title: ▄▀▄▀▄▀ [ANN] [ICO] FLUZCOIN - THE INTELLIGENT RETAIL CURRENCY ▀▄▀▄▀▄
Body: Fluzcoin relation to Fluz Fluz    We have received numerous questions and doubts from some of you — “What are the differences between Fluzcoin and Fluz Fluz?”; “Are they the same projects? (a totally wrong statement, by the way)”. So, to avoid any further misunderstandings, let's get to it and clear things up!  Fluz Fluz is a consumer cash back network that operates in Colombia and will launch in the United States, while Fluzcoin is designed to be a retail cryptocurrency that solves the problems of speed, cost, compliance and excess volatility in payment process. It is a separate business with a wholly independent management team. Fluz Fluz will serve as one of the first promoters of Fluzcoin.  More specifically, Fluz Fluz will use Fluzcoin as the central cash-back unit to be obtained from consumers participating in its daily consumption based cash back model. Thereby a natural demand for Fluzcoin is generated. In Fluz Fluz network cash-backs are calculated on fiat basis meaning Fluz Fluz will issue Fluzcoins based on the most current Fluzcoin / USD rate.  Fluz Fluz will gradually draw the rewards in Fluzcoin from a reserved lot of 6.30% of the initial Fluzcoins. This process adequately reflects the supportive but not decisive role of Fluz Fluz for Fluzcoin. Once this initial coin lot is entirely drawn, Fluz Fluz will purchase the necessary Fluzcoins at a market rate equal to other Fluzcoin holders and allocate the coin for its members’ consumption.  So, Fluzcoin and Fluz Fluz are two completely different projects. That said, Fluz Fluz will serve as one of the first promoters of Fluzcoin https://medium.com/@fluzcoin/fluzcoin-relation-to-fluz-fluz-ae42274bd3a

Title: ▄▀▄▀▄▀ [ANN] [ICO] FLUZCOIN - THE INTELLIGENT RETAIL CURRENCY ▀▄▀▄▀▄
Body: More specifically, Fluz Fluz will use Fluzcoin as the central cash-back unit to be obtained from consumers participating in its daily consumption based cash back model. Thereby a natural demand for Fluzcoin is generated. In Fluz Fluz network cash-backs are calculated on fiat basis meaning Fluz Fluz will issue Fluzcoins based on the most current Fluzcoin / USD rate.  Fluz Fluz will gradually draw the rewards in Fluzcoin from a reserved lot of 6.30% of the initial Fluzcoins. This process adequately reflects the supportive but not decisive role of Fluz Fluz for Fluzcoin. Once this initial coin lot is entirely drawn, Fluz Fluz will purchase the necessary Fluzcoins at a market rate equal to other Fluzcoin holders and allocate the coin for its members’ consumption

Author: Fluzcoin
Title: ▄▀▄▀▄▀ [ANN] [ICO] FLUZCOIN - THE INTELLIGENT RETAIL CURRENCY ▀▄▀▄▀▄
Body: THE INTELLIGENT RETAIL CURRENCY   https://i.imgur.com/KENry9h.png    Fluzcoin, as an independent retail coin structured in computer-aided governance, solves the problems of speed, cost, compliance and excess volatility; ushering in a true retail coin ready for mass adoption.  Fluzcoin’s Artificial Intelligence (AI) algorithm, EUNOMIA, overcomes crypto-economic volatility with real-time, computer-aided market corrections to the Fluzcoin supply and demand.  The value generated by minting new Fluzcoins is maximized by Fluzcoin holders in the form of proof of stake; meaning the accumulation of Fluzcoin, results in an appreciation path similar to traditional cryptocurrencies even though the value of an individual Fluzcoin may never skyrocket.   https://i.imgur.com/Uf1hf8a.png https://i.imgur.com/53vsDWG.png https://i.imgur.com/1D3j11d.png https://i.imgur.com/yPMDIl1.png https://i.imgur.com/7oRwbmn.png https://i.imgur.com/ws22Ifx.png https://i.imgur.com/mwKCr4B.png https://i.imgur.com/OADKUdt.png https://i.imgur.com/NKHMhz2.png https://i.imgur.com/IR79UQO.png   https://i.imgur.com/RjFTVwX.png  https://i.imgur.com/ut2PqKS.png     https://i.imgur.com/79gVe0p.png     https://i.imgur.com/9naIHR4.png     https://i.imgur.com/lTGPcPt.png     https://i.imgur.com/tMjoXrs.png     https://i.imgur.com/fVFnJN0.png
